    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have seriously got to see this absolute gem! It's in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
