    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies the most discerning collector's standards. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, featuring deep, lustrous paint with a high-end ceramic coating and zero chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory scent, with no visible wear on the bolsters or stitching. All electronics, switches, and displays function perfectly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, accompanied by a thick binder of documented service records from authorized specialists. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the top side. This sale includes both original master keys, all owner's manuals in their leather folio, the original window sticker, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved piece of automotive excellence that requires nothing but a new home.",
